In [Release Notes 3.0-m7 ("Milestone 7")|http://confluence.atlassian.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=214861633] we can see that it was chosen to show all the updates of a page. It's better for tracking, I think.

However, in many customers, the Confluence instance has too many updates per day, and many of them are done by different users. Therefore, they may want to choose to show only the last update of a page.

